ps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-0pKVOmILRg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-0pKVOmILRg&d=J905N8VzsThzpFTMnrW4iDANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=7ebf726d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-0pKVOmILRg</a> 9月尾, Trump<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JONpQS2h1j0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJONpQS2h1j0&d=J905N8VzsThzpFTMnrW4iDANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=4754c7a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JONpQS2h1j0</a> 10月頭, Pence"},{"pid":"9d3aba7c49f6d2a7d26c4456c5ae5104050d98d7","tid":878225,"uid":15880,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T06:28:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/27/142758_ee7f0692a9653e5cc63b8caed45bf63f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F27%2F142758_ee7f0692a9653e5cc63b8caed45bf63f.gif&h=ec86db6d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c286bbff69b5b7e7911aa8628176f81cc4bd8fb","tid":878225,"uid":56321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1438f81e54b88305651bd2c87d2c8029ed62c4ac","tid":878225,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T04:39:21.000Z","msg":"關鍵說客<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180429/large/1525015211_be97.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180429%2Flarge%2F1525015211_be97.jpg&h=344c018e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T06:38:56.000Z","msg":"兩個樣好似「懶醒嘅傻仔」"},{"pid":"9d9eaaf5cc65ebc768316a09575913b0bf72e35d","tid":878225,"uid":4258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65f91860543858492347b62e6a6d38da29af7163","tid":878225,"uid":184679,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"2fc1695c421e605e45e79f657ca1785645e0e2f3","tid":878225,"uid":35790,"like"